[2] Wold of Rohan – To discourage the opponents from running<br />
[3] Barrows of Edoras – To cycle my hand and set up the fellowship faster<br />
[4] Westemnet Hills – Because it costs 3 and is not a battleground (Uruk-hai) <br />
[5] Helm’s Gate – My minions with scimitars are stronger<br />
